title: ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code (2000)
description:
The ASME Boiler and Pressure Vessel Code
1998 Base with 1999 and 2000 Addenda

First of all, it&#039;s not about Harry Potter, it&#039;s very technical information :)

It&#039;s assumed that you have already purchased the printed version
of the Code (or any part of it). This is quite outdated version for those of you
who wants to have general impression before buying this expensive
thing.

This is old version, so never use it for real engineering! 
Buy the latest edition at http://www.asme.org/Codes/

Of course, this is copyrighted material even if it&#039;s an old version, so
don&#039;t print it or distribute. Remember, you read this as a book in 
a public library.

Have a nice reading!
